    • create

      public Registry<T> create()
      Creates a new registry from this builder. Use NewRegistryEvent.create(RegistryBuilder) or DeferredRegister.makeRegistry(Consumer) to not have to call this manually. All created registries must be registered, see NewRegistryEvent.register(Registry).
      返回:
      the created registry
      另请参阅:
